preference.name: SS1_DASS_size_default_max
preference.preference_description: Defines the default maximum value for the size similarity search (in percents) used by the Shape Search solution in the Active Workspace client. Objects with a similarity factor upper than this value will not be part of search results. The value cannot be upper than the floor value specified by the "SS1_DASS_size_upper_limit" preference. If it is, the value from this latter preference will prevail.
